abstract_ssm: The JDub Records Archive consists of materials compiled and collected by the JDub Records, a not-for-profit organization that forges vibrant connections to Judaism through music, media and cultural events. These archive documents the running of the office, the selection of and work with artists, planning of events, and other functions of JDub Records, and comprises press materials, adminstrative and financial records, and audiovisual elements.
